des: "All the great flavor of a cheeseburger is in this easy dinner that's oven ready in 15 minutes. Broccoli & Cheese Veggie Tots make a crisp and delicious topping and they add an extra serving of veggies."
ins:
Preheat oven to 425 degrees F.
Brown ground beef and onion in large skillet and drain. Stir in ketchup, pickle and mustard and bring to a boil over medium-high heat.
Reduce heat to low and simmer 5 minutes. Stir in 1 cup cheese and tomato.
Turn mixture into 1-1/2 quart baking dish and sprinkle with remaining cheese. Evenly arrange Green GiantÂ®  Broccoli & Cheese Veggie Totsâ„¢ over mixture.
Bake 20 minutes or until bubbling.  Garnish, if desired, with shredded lettuce and chopped tomato.
